  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This large randomized double-blind clinical trial (esmolol vs placebo) will enroll patients
      undergoing cardiac surgery to study the additive cardiac protection of this therapeutic
      strategy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
